text: José Antonio Rodríguez Martínez (born 23 May 1968) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Asturian sportspeople
